<arggraph id="micro_c121" topic_id="nuclear_energy_safe" stance="pro">
  <edu id="e1"><![CDATA[Nuclear energy has been proven time and time again to be safe.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e2"><![CDATA[It has been proven, over six decades, to have a minimal impact on the environment,]]></edu>
  <edu id="e3"><![CDATA[as they emit almost no greenhouse gases.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e4"><![CDATA[The chances of anything untoward happening to a nuclear facility are also slim.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e5"><![CDATA[There have been a few nuclear events since Chernobyl,]]></edu>
  <edu id="e6"><![CDATA[but there have been relatively few fatalities associated with it.]]></edu>
